        challengeConnection: { challengeId: "banking-discovery-001", text: "The Banking Discovery challenge is the exam version of the Vela story. Everything in this curriculum — problem framing, stakeholder analysis, elicitation, requirements, governance, evaluation — comes together in that challenge. It is not a test of memory. It is a test of whether you can do the work." },
